Account Deletion Instructions

Last updated: November 19, 2025

If you no longer wish to use our services, you can permanently delete your account at any time. Follow the step-by-step instructions below to remove your account and all associated data.

Step-by-Step Guide

  • Step 1: Open the app and ensure you are logged into your account.
  • Step 2: Navigate to the Home page.
  • Step 3: Go to the Profile section.
  • Step 4: Tap on My Account.
  • Step 5: Select the Delete Account option.
  • Step 6: Enter your Password and confirm your password.
  • Step 7: Tap Confirm Delete to permanently delete your account.

What Happens After Deleting Your Account?

  • Your account will be permanently removed from our system.
  • All personal data, preferences, and saved content will be deleted.
  • You will be logged out automatically.
  • This action cannot be undone.
Important:
Once your account is deleted, all your data will be permanently erased and cannot be recovered. If you need any assistance, please contact our support team before proceeding.
